 first tracks on a slope or, again paradoxically, to cross/descend a slope
 
\emph on
before
\emph default
 the presence of other parties can make the slope more hazardous, can concentrat
e parties in small areas.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Reduced visibility
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
